{"tid":1015740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[XYZ]【醫護壓力】團體到特首辦交逾萬簽名促減單程證　批社協模糊焦點","createTime":"2019-02-10T09:20:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-10T16:21:38.000Z","uid":51271,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9ccd75e3b5c7e25243641ef0c74078dbb0743c1b","tid":1015740,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:20:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">XYZ真係ID都唔駛check一定係支那污染物</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190210/s00001/1549787390640/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190210%2Fs00001%2F1549787390640%2F&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BAqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=6e201752\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190210%2Fs00001%2F1549787390640%2F&h=d64aa809\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190210/s00001/1549787390640/</a><br />\n<br />\n社會近日出現公營醫療系統和新移民的爭議，立法會議員范國威與人口政策關注組召集人譚凱邦等十多人，今午到特首辦外請願，並遞交1.2萬個簽名聯署，當中包括市民、醫護人員及十多個團體的簽名，要求減單程證，以紓緩醫療壓力。請願團體手持由簽名砌成的「減單程證」字眼，又製作「第七七七籤」的「下籤」籤詩道具，一度貼在特首辦門口，要求減單程證配額和收回移民審批權。<br />\n<br />\n發起團體人口政策關注組召集人譚凱邦指，請願的目的是聲援受壓的醫護人員，又稱新移民雖然不是公立醫院「逼爆」的唯一原因，但屬主要原因。他點名批評社協所指的歧視是模糊焦點，又以升降機比喻指，已滿載的升降機如果讓更多人進入便會超載，反問這是否歧視未進入的人。他認為因無法掌握新移民的身體狀況，故香港無法規劃醫療方面的資源運用，強調減單程證是香港人的新年願望。<br />\n<br />\n衛生服務界選委吳志傑現於威爾斯親王醫院擔任放射治療師，他不認同社協稱沒有證據顯示新移民是逼爆公院主因的說法。他認為不需要證據，因新移民不可能全部去私家醫院求診。他續指，平日工作經常會服務水泉澳邨的新移民，又要核實病人身分證，10個病人中有6至7個的名字是拼音。"},{"pid":"e2fc74369d5875b421f48e76107ad98887836d94","tid":1015740,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:49:41.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"0f8c1cf5902909981283e607df228a13e7e9ee67","tid":1015740,"uid":26770,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T10:16:16.000Z","msg":"民主黨元老菜賤昌係社協高層<br />\n<br />\n叫偽本土派gary fan開民主黨波再講"},{"pid":"e29ed817c40fbb0ebd5cfbad4a5a06d2bc9cb406","tid":1015740,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T10:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"400eb20331d579b1664f8c4f14c3425366e2f65f","tid":1015740,"uid":191833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f8c1cf5902909981283e607df228a13e7e9ee67","tid":1015740,"uid":26770,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T10:16:16.000Z","msg":"民主黨元老菜賤昌係社協高層<br />\n<br />\n叫偽本土派gary fan開民主黨波再講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T10:50:32.000Z","msg":"Gary Fan 得把口"},{"pid":"fa98fb14d05907c3a53274282f9555ea1b26af10","tid":1015740,"uid":53026,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T10:53:57.000Z","msg":"其餘三至四個只不過改咗做港式拼音扮香港人"},{"pid":"58c364c2fcc9cf73db4ed30814d5894b37db7fbb","tid":1015740,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T10:58:46.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"ca3d8f380797ec264a8ad29a24c7283bd772039a","tid":1015740,"uid":33263,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T11:17:25.000Z","msg":"Deport them"},{"pid":"aa3663dec00ee9e8544bbc040402c2f13e3d559a","tid":1015740,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T13:18:37.000Z","msg":"竟然係范國威<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ae43c8a4124e902500810e6c5c16b947a7a9cd","tid":1015740,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T14:03:57.000Z","msg":"醫護日日睇住人入醫院唔準過社協啲離地數據？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"133cf80a111e8b03ff6fcbc076db7e75f59549f3","tid":1015740,"uid":220701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T14:09:00.000Z","msg":"Y字未必係<br />\n例如邱"},{"pid":"efe17e2e5d9b08c8b5cd293b7cb9ecb650792203","tid":1015740,"uid":42879,"like"